    "role": "Credibility assessment team",
    "outcome": "Accepted",
    "rationale": "The credibility assessment for COU2 VAD hemolysis prediction has been reviewed. All 13 credibility factors have been evaluated against MRL 5 requirements. Seven factors were formally assessed with achieved levels below required levels; six factors remain as epistemic gaps. Monte Carlo UQ on boundary conditions is complete. The assessment package is accepted as a complete record of the current credibility state, acknowledging that the model does not yet meet submission requirements and further development is needed.",
